<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<section class="page-header">
  <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
  <h1 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(38px,5.6vw,68px);line-height:1.0;max-width:900px;">A marketing &amp; AI agency for businesses that refuse to blend in.</h1>
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:48px;align-items:start;max-width:900px;">
    <p class="body-text">Most businesses are held back by the same things: a brand that looks smaller than it is, weak visibility where buyers search, and manual work that eats their time. We fix all of it &mdash; branding, search and AI visibility, custom automation, and the strategy to tie it together.</p>
    <p class="body-text" style="color:var(--text-muted);">Whether it&rsquo;s a rebrand, getting cited across ChatGPT and Google AI Overviews, or a custom AI build, you get one accountable team. No hedging, no jargon-fog. Claims made and backed with numbers.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--top-border">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted" style="margin-bottom:44px;">How we operate</div>
    <div class="grid-seam grid-seam--auto">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="tile__title">Fearless</h3>
        <p class="tile__body" style="flex:none;">We make claims and back them. No hedging, no jargon-fog — just a clear point of view on what it takes to win.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="tile__title">Direct</h3>
        <p class="tile__body" style="flex:none;">Short sentences. Plain words. The point, first. You&rsquo;ll always know exactly what we&rsquo;re doing and why.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="tile__title">Proof-led</h3>
        <p class="tile__body" style="flex:none;">Numbers, citations, outcomes. Visibility you can measure — and a report that ties every effort to results.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--top-border">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-seam grid-seam--auto-sm">
      <div class="card" style="padding:30px 28px;">
        <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Category</div>
        <div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;">Branding, visibility, AI &amp; automation</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:30px 28px;">
        <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Promise</div>
        <div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;">Unstoppable visibility</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:30px 28px;">
        <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Based in</div>
        <div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;">Silicon Slopes, Utah</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--top-border">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:960px;">
    <p style="margin:0;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(28px,4.4vw,52px);line-height:1.18;letter-spacing:-0.02em;text-wrap:balance;">&ldquo;Look the part. Get found. <span style="color:var(--accent);">Get chosen.</span>&rdquo;</p>
    <p style="margin:26px 0 0;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-faint);">The Fearless Rhino promise</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/faq') %>

<section class="cta-band section--top-border">
  <div class="cta-band__inner">
    <h2>Work with a team that means it.</h2>
    <p>Book a strategy call and let&rsquo;s make your brand the answer.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book a strategy call</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
